OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'People call us the Ghosts 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof Bakhmut'                
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ukrainian forces are trying to retake  
OL,6, the city of Bakhmut in the country's   
OL,7, east. The BBC was given exclusive      
OL,8, access to a team of elite snipers,     
OL,9, referred to as "the Ghosts of Bakhmut",
OL,10, who are conducting night raids nearby. 
OL,12,FGhost, the sniping team's commander,   
OL,13,Ftakes us to the place he calls the     
OL,14,F"edge of existence" - their base on the
OL,15,Foutskirts of the city.                 
OL,17,F"Ghost is my call sign" he tells me.   
OL,18,F"When we started bringing terror to    
OL,19,FBakhmut, we got the name 'the Ghosts of
OL,20,FBakhmut'."                             
